Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.32,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\bord0.5\be5\fad(200,0)}「做好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.66,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\bord0.5\be5\fad(200,0)}「我也是」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.83,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\bord0.5\be5}「这个  给你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他们俩起得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多得去叫他们起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的  搞得这么硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  早上偶尔会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上硬邦邦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不帮你就完全收拾不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快点干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不纯异性交往…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是同性但是近亲就更加不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌  直接说头发睡乱了要弄平不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得我还以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一马跟步一起的时候  步幅比平时要小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是配合步的步幅调整的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么哦…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的你还真是够精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的兄弟精神还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  早上好  大吾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…一马同学  差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一  大吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和日向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你这副厌恶的表情算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有摆什么厌恶的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你别想蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好像感觉有谁在盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开饭了开饭了开饭了啊  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开饭了开饭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}买了面包就快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不初等不及会口水流一桌子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会  我带好手帕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不否定会流口水啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  传闻中从都市转学来的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山里面突然把女孩子推倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  是有这传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像流传着一些不太好的谣传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从都市来的转学生已经够引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还搞出了那种事  想没谣传都难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那是个误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次三次还不够  足足干了五次对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（注：日语里误会和五次读音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个五次啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南国原老师的班会总是那么久真烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要不去哪儿逛逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午吃了那么多都饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你摆出副「这家伙在说啥我不懂」的表情来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是初啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在暗处偷看别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  你好像是神社的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你突然这样让我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然突然冲过来然后把我抱住我觉得还是有很多不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎要干这种事也需要按顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是太突然了让我很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是不是应该把手  把手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一马？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性恐惧症？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说虽然有点夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过圆佳因为被爷爷管得太严
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以似乎不太擅长和男性相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被不太熟悉的人突然接触的话就会陷入混乱状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像刚才那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚  大概是一种护身术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是爷爷为了不让害虫靠近而让她学的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你遭殃了  不过也别因为这个而讨厌圆佳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  一马果然很温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够贪睡的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经快中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是星期天你也太懒散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  昨晚睡晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步早就出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着素描本去写生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一马也快点吃了早饭去散散步什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆这会碍着打扫房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去哪散步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过天气挺好  在附近随便逛逛好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…腰还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性恐惧症？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆佳因为被爷爷管得太严
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以似乎不太擅长和男性相处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是我不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去道个歉比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  不在  在  不在  在  不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  在了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  之前真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个…我才是  对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起  我没想要做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神的时候身体就自己动起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那时候都怪我突然抓着你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是神本同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  你能这么说我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  叫我圆佳就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星野同学是前辈  就请这么叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我一马就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的前辈…一马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么圆佳  我差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  我有事想问前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是有事想问一马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想问？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  虽然不知道这种事该不该问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和中津川前辈的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你在山里面推倒了她  然后做了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:13:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  在那河里踏石的地方滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  想向着岸边大步跳过去却滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时侯也经常到那去玩  也滑倒过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以跟初的那个是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多事也是谣传…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  虽然确实是接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是滑倒时顺势推倒了她才偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  跟中津川前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等等  为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天在唤  地在唤  人在唤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶即斩在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是藤堂小依
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为制裁罪恶而在此登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市的害虫星野一马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为害这山比古镇和平的你不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  突然冒出来把人叫成害虫是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁什么时候为害和平了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装蒜了星野一马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对阿初下毒手的事我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿初？  难道你是在说初吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那是误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会吗  那现在你把圆佳弄哭的事该怎么交代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…我也搞不清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手小依
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是我自己哭出来而已  不能怪一马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托了  不要这样对一马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星野一马  这次就看在圆佳的面子上饶了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是你再敢弄哭圆佳下次我就不会再饶你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  听到「咚隆」就要闭上眼蹲下才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我怎么退场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…你跟我说这些小朋友的角色扮演规则…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚隆  咚隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  今天放学顺便去Bacpipe吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我Pass了  今天有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那阿一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来日向你在什么社团啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹是练弓道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓道？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常厉害  人称比古南的罗宾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾…  什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  是罗宾汉啦罗宾汉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然被人这么称呼那一定是真的很厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  都已经被选为下次县大会的代表了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这种事都无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是这样的话放学就变成初和兄弟独处了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  大吾也有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天  要留下来英语补课
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是该耍酷说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你敢趁放学跟初独处对她做什么奇怪的事  我不会饶你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  日向那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的事是什么意思啊  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹真是净说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  还有初姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我进美术部了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  因为步画画很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那下次我给你做模特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步帮我画一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我画得不是很好  怎么敢要模特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步  你脸有点红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没有啦  我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把额头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看有没有发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦  在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有点发烧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  你身子那么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不小心拖重了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我背你回万代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦  我能自己走回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初  不好意思包就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步  发烧了不能勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我小时候也经常让哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚好痛  走不动了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我背你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想像那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  我竟然在步发烧的时候想这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  步的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了感冒药  钻进被窝在我拉着他的手的时候睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天就会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  没出什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一真是个好哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步真让人羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这不是说我想让阿一背下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用额头碰额头什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  还真是打扰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两位  请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------NEXT----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂一马  你喜欢什么类型的女孩啊？
